sequenceDiagram
  participant I as Ingest Service
  participant C as Chain Store
  participant W as Window Policy
  participant G as Seal Generator
  participant V as Verifier

  I->>C: Append Event (namespace_id, chain_id, sequence)
  C-->>I: Event accepted
  C->>W: Evaluate window trigger
  W-->>G: Window closed (start_seq, end_seq)
  G->>C: Read window Events in canonical order
  G->>G: Compute window_commitment_hash
  G->>G: Build seal input S
  G->>G: Compute seal_hash and sign
  G->>C: Persist Seal (namespace_id, chain_id, window_id)
  V->>C: Fetch Seal and window Events
  V->>V: Recompute commitment and seal_hash
  V-->>V: PASS if linkage and signature valid
